LGBT Wellness Summit ( June 5 - 12, 2017 ) ➡️
http://tinyurl.com/m7tsv9y
LGBT people struggle with health challenges at a much higher rate than the rest of society — it’s time do something about it!
The world’s most inspiring coaches, leaders, doctors and specialists are here to address the health needs of the transgender, gay, lesbian and bisexual community!
Suicide, mental illness, obesity, alcoholism, drug abuse, injuries, violence, HIV/AIDS (and other health issues) all deeply affect the LGBT community. We believe our community can (and should) be one of good health, personal growth and confident transformation. Therefore, our experts at this event will provide support and clarity for you, your friends and your family members to create, repair and strengthen the important relationships in your life, including the one you have with yourself!
Join this summit if you’re struggling with “coming out,” living in judgment, enduring a fragmented family, looking for meaning and acceptance, or want to live a healthier, happier life. With the educational and actionable steps learned from this event, you’ll gain much-needed expertise to help you move forward in all aspects of your life ➡️ http://tinyurl.com/m7tsv9y
SHARE the link with friends and family so that we can all learn together.
